message.body: Hey Geoff. I wanted to plan a trip down to baltimore. Maybe November 22 23 or December 6 7th. Will you be available? I could bring down the piece to you
I think December will be better for me as I have to travel for thanksgiving
we'll be here on the 7th, the night of Friday into Saturday we'll be down in d.c. but back midday Saturday so I can drop some work to a show. how'd the asbury park show go?
Pretty good. I think I sold some small stuff and they are taking some work to Miami in December
Is November better? I'll have to check with Lindsey but I'd be staying at phill's anyway
pretty sure we're around both days that weekend. either way is fine
